At the 2000 International CES, January 6-9, 2000 in Las Vegas, Nevada. It's where savvy buyers and consumers look for technologies that will enhance their lifestyles. Technological advances occur almost daily, from semi-conductor chips to home theater to DTV, DSS, wireless and video. Buyers want to work these products into their sales and distribution channels. And they need you at CES to do it!<br>


		
